step('7', 8, 'loosen the mix up with a splash of noodle water.'). 
step('7', 9, 'then add your udon to the sauce and season well with salt and pepper.'). 
step('7', 10, 'squeeze in half a lemon.'). 
step('7', 11, 'stir your noodles gently you get a thick, glossy sauce and give it a good shake in the pan.'). 
