step('177', 20, 'season with salt and pepper.'). 
step('177', 21, 'ladle your soup into bowls and top with your crispy chilli, garlic and parsley.'). 
step('177', 22, 'next, youre going to want to layer on your reserved roasted cauliflower florets and crispy potatoes along a drizzle of tahini and a sprinkling of sumac.'). 
