step('178', 13, 'slowly drizzle in the olive oil whilst blending and then season with salt and pepper.'). 
step('178', 14, 'chop up the mozzarella into 18 large chunks and grate the cheddar.'). 
step('178', 15, 'knock back the dough and divide it into 18 equal-sized pieces - you will need to weigh these on scales.'). 
step('178', 16, 'flatten each piece of dough and place a dollop of pesto and a big cube of mozzarella in the middle.'). 
step('178', 17, 'pinch the edges together to close up the mozzarella and roll into a ball.'). 
step('178', 18, 'grease a baking dish with butter.'). 
step('178', 19, 'arrange your rolls inside the dish seam-side down, then sprinkle with your grated cheddar.'). 
step('178', 20, 'cover and leave to rise for an hour.'). 
step('178', 21, 'heat your oven to 200c.'). 
step('178', 22, 'bake for 25 mins until puffed and golden.'). 
step('178', 23, 'for the garlic butter, finely chop the chives and parsley.'). 
step('178', 24, 'melt the butter in a microwave and grate in three cloves of garlic.'). 
step('178', 25, 'season with salt.'). 
step('178', 26, 'once the dough balls are out of the oven, brush liberally with the garlic butter and serve hot.'). 
