step('248', 1, 'the day before eating, combine all of the dry brine ingredients - thats your salt, sugar, fennel seeds, coriander seeds, cumin seeds, onion granules and garlic granules - in a shallow tray.'). 
step('248', 2, 'make sure theyre mixed together nicely.'). 
step('248', 3, 'liberally sprinkle the brine over the pork slices, making sure to get seasoning on every crevice.'). 
step('248', 4, 'cover and place in your fridge overnight.'). 
step('248', 5, 'this process will not only help give the pork flavour all the way through, but also changes the texture to ensure you get nice juicy pork.'). 
