step('262', 15, 'tip your vegetable paste into the same pan and cook for a few mins until fragrant.'). 
step('262', 16, 'add your flour and cook out for 2 mins, stirring until you have a smooth paste.'). 
step('262', 17, 'gradually pour in your chicken stock, whisking constantly so you have a smooth base.'). 
