step('327', 4, 'push the pieces of garlic into the tomatoes, then sprinkle with oregano and salt.'). 
step('327', 5, 'roast for 30-45 mins until charred.'). 
step('327', 6, 'push on them gently halfway through to press out the liquid from the tomatoes.'). 
