step('328', 3, 'pour your flour and 65ml hot water into a bowl and mix until you have a shaggy dough.'). 
step('328', 4, 'knead until smooth, then cover in a damp tea towel and rest for 20 mins.'). 
step('328', 5, 'finely slice your leek, dice your mushrooms, slice your spring onions, and grate your garlic and ginger.'). 
