step('335', 6, 'heat up a frying pan to a high heat, allow it to warm up for 2 mins.'). 
step('335', 7, 'pinch off a golf ball-sized piece of dough and liberally dust your work surface with flour.'). 
step('335', 8, 'roll the dough gently into a small circle and then coat it again with flour.'). 
step('335', 9, 'continue rolling until you form a thin circle that is about 15cm in diameter.'). 
step('335', 10, 'place the rotli face-side down in the frying pan.'). 
