step('345', 21, 'once all the milk is added, bring the mixture to a boil and allow it to thicken.'). 
step('345', 22, 'add your cheddar and season to taste with salt and pepper.'). 
step('345', 23, 'pour a little white sauce into the base of your baking dish, followed by a little ragu.'). 
step('345', 24, 'arrange your lasagna sheets neatly on top, snapping sheets where necessary to plug the gaps.'). 
step('345', 25, 'pour over 1/3rd of your remaining ragu followed by 1/3rd of your remaining sauce, then more lasagna sheets.'). 
step('345', 26, 'continue like this until you are out of all your mixtures.'). 
step('345', 27, 'mix the top layer so that the ragu and white sauce combine, pushing it all the way to the edges so the lasagna sheets are totally covered.'). 
