step('370', 16, 'add your chopped tomatoes, porcini mushroom stock, chopped porcini, shredded oyster mushrooms, marmite and bay leaf to the pan.'). 
step('370', 17, 'give it a good mix and bring the mixture to a boil.'). 
step('370', 18, 'turn down the heat and simmer for an hour.'). 
step('370', 19, 'heat a generous glug of olive oil in a frying pan.'). 
