step('512', 18, 'on to the greek salad.'). 
step('512', 19, 'roughly chop the tomatoes, cucumber and other salad veggies.'). 
step('512', 20, 'pour in the red wine vinegar, 1 tsp of oregano and a good glug of olive oil and add your olives.'). 
step('512', 21, 'season with salt and pepper.'). 
step('512', 22, 'set aside.'). 
step('512', 23, 'once the chicken is done, transfer to a plate, cover loosely with foil and let rest.'). 
step('512', 24, 'flour your surface.'). 
step('512', 25, 'cut the dough into 8 pieces.'). 
step('512', 26, 'roll each into a rough ball with your hands.'). 
step('512', 27, 'then, using a rolling pin, roll into oval flatbreads 1/2 cm thick.'). 
step('512', 28, 'get a large griddle hot, or cook on your bbq.'). 
step('512', 29, 'in batches, cook the flatbreads for 2 minutes on each side.'). 
