step('515', 1, 'rinse the bulgur wheat until the water runs clear.'). 
step('515', 2, 'cook in a pan of boiling salted water (3 parts liquid) and simmer until absorbed.'). 
step('515', 3, 'meanwhile, chop the tomatoes in half, remove any stems and spoon out the seeds so you are left with just the flesh.'). 
step('515', 4, 'finely dice the flesh then scoop up the tomatoes and drain away any excess moisture.'). 
step('515', 5, 'place into a large mixing bowl.'). 
step('515', 6, 'finely chop the spring onion and add into the bowl.'). 
step('515', 7, 'squeeze in the juice and zest of a lemon and season with salt and pepper.'). 
step('515', 8, 'mix everything together.'). 
