step('515', 14, 'keep adding water splash by splash until you have a nice creamy tahini dressing.'). 
step('515', 15, 'slice the halloumi into thin chunks and add into a bowl.'). 
step('515', 16, 'season with olive oil, salt and pepper.'). 
step('515', 17, 'heat a non-stick frying pan on a medium-high heat and whack in the halloumi.'). 
step('515', 18, 'fry each piece of halloumi on both sides until golden brown and set aside.'). 
step('515', 19, 'while the halloumi is frying, finely chop your herbs (mint and parsley).'). 
step('515', 20, 'it is important not to bruise them so try to chop them as finely as possible on the first chop through so that you dont have to go back and forth lots of times.'). 
