step('515', 22, 'add the herbs and the spices (cinnamon and ground coriander) into the bulgur and tomato bowl.'). 
step('515', 23, 'season with salt, pepper, a tbsp olive oil and toss together.'). 
step('515', 24, 'immediately serve up the herby tabbouleh (you dont want to leave it sitting around for too long).'). 
step('515', 25, 'top with your golden halloumi, and drizzle on the tahini dressing.'). 
step('515', 26, 'scatter each plate with a few pomegranate seeds, season and enjoy!.'). 
