step('529', 3, 'if needed, add a dash more water or flour.'). 
step('529', 4, 'leave the dough to rest for 20 minutes.'). 
step('529', 5, 'knead the dough.'). 
step('529', 6, 'do this by placing the fingertips of one hand into the dough then pushing the dough away with the other.'). 
step('529', 7, 'fold the dough back onto itself, then repeat the process.'). 
step('529', 8, 'do this for a few minutes.'). 
step('529', 9, 'form 16 evenly sized balls from the dough.'). 
