step('665', 2, 'leave this to soak for 20 minutes.'). 
step('665', 3, 'meanwhile, you can start prepping the base of your biryani.'). 
step('665', 4, 'begin by cutting your onion in half then finely slicing both pieces so youre left with little onion crescents.'). 
