step('734', 3, 'mix well so that they are all evenly coated.'). 
step('734', 4, 'leave at room temp for 30-45 minutes, depending on how much time you have.'). 
step('734', 5, 'get your dredging station ready.'). 
step('734', 6, 'mix the remaining spices, salt, plain flour and cornflour in a bowl.'). 
step('734', 7, 'in a separate bowl, crack in 1 egg, whisk and stir in the buttermilk.'). 
step('734', 8, 'have a baking tray ready for your coated chicken.'). 
